    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-stone-900 mb-10 text-center font-normal font-serif" style="font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;">Pourquoi le format change la donne</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-5 text-stone-700 text-lg font-medium">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
